page.title: 06Mr Breeds (contd)
page.content: She had her "jelly bean" shoes on, they are quite fashionable but{Mr {Little}thinks they aren't very suitable for walking as they are made of plastic. { Mr Breeds}challenged us to run down the steepest of the sand dunes and turn around at the bottom and run back up again.{Jason Smith}set a new primary school record of 28 seconds. Towards the end of the walk we looked at an artificial pond, it didn't look man made as it blended in with the surrounding area. We saw lots of{ {Dragonflies, Newts}and{Water Beetles.} (There was so much to see we will write lists later in the text for further information, see pages 12_13).
